# FILE: businessDashboard/businessDashboard.desc
# ROLE: Business Account Control Panel (NEW)
# ROUTE: /business
# ACCOUNT: Business only — students/admins redirect to their dashboards
# THEME: Dark · bg-[#0F1828] cards · colored tabs per business type

## DESIGN
- LAYOUT: sidebar (desktop) + main area — same structure as /admin but lighter palette
- SIDEBAR: business logo + name + businessType badge + nav links
- TOP BAR: account status pill (🟢 نشط / 🕒 قيد المراجعة / 🔴 مجمّد)

## SUB-DASHBOARDS BY BUSINESS TYPE

### A. VENDOR (بائع منتجات) → businessType === 'vendor'
- NAV: المنتجات · الطلبات · الإيرادات · الإعدادات
- PRODUCTS TAB:
  - Grid of listed products (same card style as /store)
  - [+ إضافة منتج] → product upload form
  - Product status: 🟢 منشور · 🕒 قيد المراجعة · 🔴 مرفوض (admin must approve)
- ORDERS TAB: incoming orders table (matches Universal Order Manager)
- REVENUE TAB: total sales · pending payouts · withdrawal request button

### B. ADVERTISER (معلن محلي) → businessType === 'advertiser'
- NAV: الحملات الإعلانية · إنشاء حملة · الأداء
- CAMPAIGNS TAB: list of submitted/active/expired ads
- CREATE CAMPAIGN:
  - Upload ad image (WebP)
  - Target URL
  - Preferred zone (header / sidebar / in-feed)
  - Campaign period (start + end date)
  - [📤 إرسال للمراجعة] → goes to admin ad console queue
- PERFORMANCE TAB: impressions · clicks · CTR per campaign

### C. EXTERNAL FREELANCER (مستقل خارجي) → businessType === 'freelancer'
- NAV: خدماتي · طلباتي · الإيرادات · الملف العام
- Same flow as student freelancer BUT under Business account
- Subscription: same $5/month via ShamCash
- Profile visible in /freelance catalog same as student freelancers
- Badge: "مستقل خارجي" (amber) vs student freelancer "مستقل طلابي" (indigo)

## STATUS FLOW
- Registration → status: 'pending' (waiting admin approval)
- Admin approves → status: 'active' → full dashboard access
- Admin freezes → status: 'frozen' → read-only + banner notification
